    "The authors gave illustrative examples.",
    "The application of a fuzzy-number-based questionnaire was introduced by Jónás et al. (2018) in order to enhance the reliability of peer evaluations.",
    "The membership function of the fuzzy number was composed of an increasing and decreasing sigmoid membership function associated with Dombi's intersection operator.",
    "This allowed peer reviewers to express their uncertainty and the variability of the reviewed person's performance in a quantitative way.",
    "A case study was offered."
